
================================================================================
              CO-PO MAPPING — HOW IT WORKS (Detailed Technical Guide)
              Multi-Agent NBA/NAAC Accreditation Intelligence System
================================================================================

This document explains, step by step, how CO-PO mapping is performed in this
system — covering both the AI (LLM) path and the manual path, the data models,
validation rules, and the PI (Performance Indicator) alignment layer.

